18 SECTION 3. A NEW SECTION OF KRS CHAPTER 138 IS CREATED TO
19 READ AS FOLLOWS:
20 (1) As used in this section:
21 (a) "Food" has the same meaning as in KRS 217.2201;
22 (b) "Hemp" means the plant species Cannabis sativa L. and any part of that
23 plant, including the seeds thereof and all derivatives, extracts,
24 cannabinoids, isomers, acids, salts, and salts of isomers, whether growing or
25 not, with a total delta-9 tetrahydrocannabinol concentration of not more
26 than three-tenths of one percent (0.3%) on a dry weight basis;
27 (c) "Hemp-derived cannabinoid product":
Page 8 of 109
HB000910.100 - 323 - XXXX 3/10/2026 3:19 PM GA

